name: @contentco/aws-cloudfront
author: Daniel Conde <danielconde9@gmail.com>
description: This package was copied from https://github.com/serverless-components/aws-cloudfront because it wasn't being maintained anymore. It is being used by the [nextjs serverless component](https://github.com/serverless-nextjs/serverless-next.js/tree/master/packages/serverless-component) to provision the CloudFront distribution behind the scenes.
